l'm not going to make a speech.

66
00:08:47,539 --> 00:08:49,439
Just got something to say.

67
00:08:51,009 --> 00:08:54,274
Tomorrow our old pal Doc here
is going out.

68
00:08:54,712 --> 00:08:57,545
He's being paid off after 30 years.

69
00:08:58,249 --> 00:09:01,275
l know most of you kids got a ways
to go before you find out...

70
00:09:01,486 --> 00:09:03,886
...what 30 years in the Navy means.

71
00:09:04,556 --> 00:09:05,989
lt means service.

72
