We'll do our best, sir.

102
00:12:31,729 --> 00:12:33,390
This just came in, sir.

103
00:12:43,141 --> 00:12:44,403
Gentlemen.

104
00:12:44,709 --> 00:12:47,234
You may assume that a state
of war exists between...

105
00:12:47,445 --> 00:12:49,572
...the United States
and the Empire of Japan.

106
00:12:49,947 --> 00:12:51,471
Govern yourselves accordingly.

107
00:12:51,916 --> 00:12:53,679
My compliments, gentlemen.

108
00:13:02,260 --> 00:13:03,784
Here are the orders.

109
