Give 1 2 to Lefty.

125
00:15:00,044 --> 00:15:01,068
Now hear this.

126
00:15:01,279 --> 00:15:04,043
Unidentified aircraft approaches Cavite.

127
00:15:04,248 --> 00:15:07,581
Unidentified aircraft
approaching Cavite.

128
