Those are Jap planes.

129
00:15:29,540 --> 00:15:30,404
Headed this way.

130
00:15:39,116 --> 00:15:41,016
All boats out in the bay.

131
00:15:41,686 --> 00:15:43,950
Follow me, and stand by for signals.

132
00:15:52,063 --> 00:15:53,291
ls that another drill?

133
00:15:53,498 --> 00:15:54,328
Can't be a drill.

134
00:15:54,532 --> 00:15:57,000
All we get in this Navy
is drill, drill, drill.

135
00:15:57,201 --> 00:15:59,396
Fire in the paint locker!

136
00:16:57,461 --> 00:16:59,053
One formation.

137
